import logo from './logo.svg'
import './App.css'
import Movies from './screen/Movies'
import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/Movies" element={Movies}></Route>
      </Routes>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
